 If you have some additional test results, feel free to open a GitHub issue to help expand this list !
 
+**Newer (12th-gen and later) units** enumerate with USB id `1038:113a` instead of the default
+`1038:1122`. If `lsusb` shows `1038:113a`, pass `--id 1038:113a` (e.g. the GS66 Stealth 12UHS / MS-16V5).
+The `GS65`/`GS66` keymap covers these 15" no-numpad Stealth layouts, so `Home`/`End` are addressable
+with `--model GS65` (or `GS66`).
